EXPRESSION:
VAR TargetCurrency = IF(
                          ISBLANK( SELECTEDVALUE (ToCurrency[To_Currency])),
                          "CAD",   -- default
                          SELECTEDVALUE (ToCurrency[To_Currency])
                        )
 RETURN
        SUMX(
             SUMMARIZE(
                    FILTER(
                           F_PurchaseOrderLine,
                           NOT ISBLANK ( F_PurchaseOrderLine[CancelDate] )
                       ),
                    D_PO_OrderDate[Date],
                    FromCurrency[From_Currency],
                    "OriginalAmountCAD", SUM(F_PurchaseOrderLine[OriginalAmount_cad])
               ),
               VAR OriginalAmountCAD = [OriginalAmountCAD]
               VAR ExchangeRate =
                   CALCULATE(
                        MAX('Currency Conversion by Date'[transaction_Mutiplicator]),
                        ToCurrency[To_Currency] = TargetCurrency
,
                        REMOVEFILTERS(D_Branch)
             )
RETURN OriginalAmountCAD * ExchangeRate
)

VAR SecondItem = 
        SUMX(
             SUMMARIZE(
                    CALCULATETABLE(F_PurchaseOrderLine, D_ItemMaster[SecondItemNumber] = "333333-2"),
                    D_PO_OrderDate[Date],
                    FromCurrency[From_Currency],
                    "OriginalAmountCAD", SUM(F_PurchaseOrderLine[OriginalAmount_cad])
               ),
               VAR OriginalAmountCAD = [OriginalAmountCAD]
               VAR ExchangeRate =
                   CALCULATE(
                        MAX('Currency Conversion by Date'[transaction_Mutiplicator]),
                        ToCurrency[To_Currency] = TargetCurrency
             )
              RETURN OriginalAmountCAD * ExchangeRate
            )

RETURN LineTypeF + SecondItem

VAR Orders =
    SUMMARIZE(
        F_PurchaseOrderLine,
        F_PurchaseOrderLine[OrderNumber]
    )
VAR OrdersWithStatus =
    ADDCOLUMNS(
        Orders,
        "__po_status",
            VAR canc  = CALCULATE([Cancelled_Line_Count])
            RETURN IF(canc > 0, "Cancelled", "Active")
    )
RETURN
COUNTROWS(
    FILTER(
        OrdersWithStatus,
        [__po_status] = "Cancelled"
    )
)

VAR Orders =
    SUMMARIZE(
        F_PurchaseOrderLine,
        F_PurchaseOrderLine[OrderNumber]
    )
VAR OrdersWithStatus =
    ADDCOLUMNS(
        Orders,
        "__po_status",
            VAR total = CALCULATE([Total_Line_Count])
            VAR canc  = CALCULATE([Cancelled_Line_Count])
            RETURN IF(total > 0 && total = canc, "Cancelled", "Active")
    )
RETURN
COUNTROWS(
    FILTER(
        OrdersWithStatus,
        [__po_status] = "Active"
    )
)

)

VAR OrdersWithAnyReceipt =
    DISTINCT (
        SELECTCOLUMNS (
            FILTER ( F_PurchaseOrderLine, NOT ISBLANK ( F_PurchaseOrderLine[ReceptionDate] ) ),
            "OrderNumber", F_PurchaseOrderLine[OrderNumber]
        )
    )
VAR OrdersWithAnyMissingReceipt =
    DISTINCT (
        SELECTCOLUMNS (
            FILTER ( F_PurchaseOrderLine, ISBLANK ( F_PurchaseOrderLine[ReceptionDate] ) ),
            "OrderNumber", F_PurchaseOrderLine[OrderNumber]
        )
    )
RETURN
    COUNTROWS ( INTERSECT ( OrdersWithAnyReceipt, OrdersWithAnyMissingReceipt ) )

 RETURN

)

VAR EarlyDeliveries = 
        COUNTROWS(
            FILTER(
                F_PurchaseOrderLine,
                NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_PromisedDeliveryDate]) &&
                NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_ReceiptDate]) &&
                F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_PromisedDeliveryDate] > F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_ReceiptDate]
            )
        )
    VAR TotalLinesWithReceiptDate = 
        COUNTROWS(
            FILTER(
                F_PurchaseOrderLine,
                NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_ReceiptDate])
            )
        )
    RETURN
        IF(
            TotalLinesWithReceiptDate > 0,
            DIVIDE(EarlyDeliveries, TotalLinesWithReceiptDate),
            BLANK()
        )

CALCULATE(
    [Active_Line_Count],
    FILTER(
        ALL('D_PO_OrderDate'),
        'D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear] = MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear])
            && 'D_PO_OrderDate'[Date] <= MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[Date])
    ),
    ISBLANK('D_PO_CancelDate'[Date])
)

CALCULATE(
    [Total_Line_Count],
    DATESYTD(
        'D_PO_OrderDate'[Date],
        "02-28" // Fiscal year ends on February 28th
    )
)

CALCULATE(
    [Active_Line_Count],
    FILTER(
        ALL('D_PO_OrderDate'),
        'D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear] = MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear]) - 1
            && 'D_PO_OrderDate'[Date] <= EDATE(MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[Date]), -12)
    ),
    ISBLANK('D_PO_CancelDate'[Date])
)

CALCULATE(
    AVERAGE('F_PurchaseOrderLine'[Leadtime_ReceiptDate]),
    FILTER(
        ALL('D_PO_OrderDate'),
        'D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear] = MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear])
            && 'D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalMonth] = MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalMonth])
            && 'D_PO_OrderDate'[Date] <= MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[Date])
    )
)

CALCULATE (
    SUMX (
        DISTINCT (
            SELECTCOLUMNS (
                F_PurchaseOrderLine,
                "ItemNumber", RELATED(D_ItemMaster[SecondItemNumber]),
                "QuantityOrder", F_PurchaseOrderLine[QuantityOrder]
            )
        ),
        [QuantityOrder]
    ),
    FILTER (
        F_PurchaseOrderLine,
        ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[ReceptionDate]) &&
        ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[CancelDate]) &&
        NOT(ISBLANK(RELATED(D_ItemMaster[SecondItemNumber])))
    )
)

CALCULATE(
    AVERAGE('Purchase Order Line'[Leadtime_JDE]),
    FILTER(
        ALL('D_PO_OrderDate'),
        'D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear] = MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear]) - 1
            && 'D_PO_OrderDate'[Date] <= EDATE(MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[Date]), -12)
    )
)

AVERAGEX(
    FILTER(
        F_PurchaseOrderLine,
        NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate]) &&
        NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_PromisedDeliveryDate])
    ),
    F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate] - F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_PromisedDeliveryDate]
)

AVERAGEX(
    FILTER(
        F_PurchaseOrderLine,
        NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate]) &&
        NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_SupplierFirstPromisedDate])
    ),
    F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate] - F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_SupplierFirstPromisedDate]
)

AVERAGEX(
    FILTER(
        F_PurchaseOrderLine,
        NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate]) &&
        NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_PromisedDeliveryDate])
    ),
    F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate] - F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_PromisedDeliveryDate]
)

CALCULATE(
    AVERAGEX(
        FILTER(
            F_PurchaseOrderLine,
            NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate]) &&
            NOT ISBLANK(F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_SupplierFirstPromisedDate])
        ),
        F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_RequestDate] - F_PurchaseOrderLine[Leadtime_SupplierFirstPromisedDate]
    ),
    'D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear] = MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[FiscalYear]) - 1 &&
    'D_PO_OrderDate'[Date] <= EDATE(MAX('D_PO_OrderDate'[Date]), -12)
)
